platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From the moment we started this ingenious strategy-RPG, we knew it was something special. It’s not just the gorgeously animated spaceships and cool Western robots. The unique trick-shot gunplay makes each battle a tactical treat full of crackerjack aiming and ricochets. We’re head over spurs for the awesome blend of exploration and bot-blasting action.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Plan your attack with robots and ricochets.
Faites ricocher vos balles pour venir à bout de vos ennemis.
